fields.name: Bright House Networks Stadium
fields.profile: The 48,000 seat Bright House Networks Football Stadium opened in 2007 and is designed for a planned expansion to 65,000 seats. UCF is the first school to ever build and open a new stadium and a new arena in the same year.
